1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:05,260 --> 00:00:07,180
When did I ever say

4
00:00:08,660 --> 00:00:10,220
I was taking you with me?

5
00:00:12,740 --> 00:00:14,780
You interrupted
my attempt to end my life

6
00:00:15,380 --> 00:00:17,100
and ruined my plans.

7
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:20,140
And now you expect me to thank you?

8
00:00:21,020 --> 00:00:22,100
Move aside.

9
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:23,980
Move.

10
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:33,060
(What's going on?)

11
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:35,500
(I just saved
another ungrateful wretch.)

12
00:00:40,740 --> 00:00:41,580
Well.

13
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,500
Not so cocky anymore, huh?

14
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:45,820
Why aren't you acting
all high and mighty now?

15
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:48,540
Done acting tough
with Prince Jing backing you up?

16
00:00:48,980 --> 00:00:50,899
Now that he's gone,

17
00:00:50,900 --> 00:00:52,700
you're

18
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:54,219
all alone.

19
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:55,219
What do you mean?

20
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:56,460
What are you trying to do?

21
00:00:56,620 --> 00:00:58,019
You little jinx,

22
00:00:58,020 --> 00:01:00,820
not a single person
in this world wants you.

23
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:04,020
You deserve to be burned alive alone

24
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:05,740
and rot in a filthy ditch.

25
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:39,540
Your...

26
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:40,460
Your Highness.

27
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:42,499
Your...

28
00:01:42,500 --> 00:01:43,180
Your Highness.

29
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:44,940
Didn't you already leave?

30
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:47,100
I've changed my mind.

31
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:53,740
You're a jinx.

32
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:55,860
And I'm a cursed star.

33
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:57,100
Perfect.

34
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:58,580
I happen to need a daughter.

35
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:01,580
Do you believe in love
at first sight with a father?

36
00:02:01,620 --> 00:02:03,379
The moment I saw you,

37
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:05,900
I knew you were meant to be my father.

38
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:10,539
From now on, my name

39
00:02:10,540 --> 00:02:12,220
is Xiao Suisui.

40
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:16,420
Since you've acknowledged me
as your father,

41
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:18,540
then harming the princess

42
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:21,220
is the same as harming royal blood.

43
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:21,939
No...

44
00:02:21,940 --> 00:02:23,060
Tell me,

45
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:25,380
how should we punish them?

46
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,339
Young Mistress,

47
00:02:32,340 --> 00:02:33,360
the Ancestor said

48
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,680
you came down to the mortal world
to change people's opinions of you,

49
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,000
not to kill people and set fires.

50
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,980
Did you forget?

51
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:39,259
(So annoying.)

52
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:41,220
(Of course I didn't forget.)

53
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:43,539
Well, Father...

54
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,939
Killing people isn't good.

55
00:02:44,940 --> 00:02:46,060
We Mystic Crows...

56
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:48,380
We should do good and build virtue.

57
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:51,899
But while they may escape death,

58
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:53,180
they won't escape punishment.

59
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:56,379
They threw me into
the mass grave for three days.

60
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:58,459
Then let them experience

61
00:02:58,460 --> 00:03:00,140
the suffering I went through.

62
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:01,180
Very well.

63
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,020
As you wish.

64
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:06,460
Your Highness. Spare us.

65
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:07,340
Three days?

66
00:03:07,380 --> 00:03:08,980
There are wild wolves at the mass grave!

67
00:03:09,140 --> 00:03:11,220
I'll die there, Your Highness!

68
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:12,619
Let's go.

69
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:13,260
Your Highness!

70
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:14,060
Your Highness!

71
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,380
Your Highness!

72
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,460
Your Highness!

73
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:20,980
Dear.

74
00:03:21,420 --> 00:03:22,260
Dear!

75
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:32,540
Those crows
followed that little jinx here!

76
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:35,420
What terrible luck.

77
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:42,979
What's that great jinx doing back here?

78
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:44,419
We're doomed to bad luck now.

79
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:46,420
She's back to bring disaster again.

80
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:04,619
Princess Xiao Suisui
has returned home with her royal father.

81
00:04:04,620 --> 00:04:06,780
Rise.

82
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,560
(Prince Jing's Manor)

83
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:17,899
Father,

84
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:19,460
didn't you say

85
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,500
you had an army of a hundred thousand?

86
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:24,340
Where are they?

87
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:33,420
Your Highness!

88
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:35,740
Your Highness!

89
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:38,020
Your Highness!

90
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:41,780
Watch out.

91
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:43,540
Your Highness!

92
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,859
(Shiwan, Steward of Prince Jing's Manor)
Your servant, Shiwan.

93
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,200
(Dajun, Guard of Prince Jing's Manor)
Your subordinate, Dajun.

94
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:50,340
Greetings, Your Highness.

95
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:54,099
Father,

96
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:55,820
aren't you a prince?

97
00:04:56,300 --> 00:04:58,820
How did things end up this miserable?

98
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:00,419
Father?

99
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:01,700
What did you just call him?

100
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,739
As expected of Prince Jing.

101
00:05:04,740 --> 00:05:07,700
Even having a daughter
happens at lightning speed.

102
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:09,979
Far beyond ordinary people.

103
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:11,249
Leaving everyone else in the dust.

104
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:12,460
Exactly.

105
00:05:13,020 --> 00:05:14,620
I picked her up on the road.

106
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:19,460
I told you long ago,

107
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:22,700
even the Imperial Preceptor
personally declared my fate.

108
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:26,020
I am doomed to bring harm
to my loved ones, a lone cursed star.

109
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,780
Because of that,

110
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:31,140
thirty thousand soldiers were buried
in the northern border,

111
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:34,100
and my leg as well...

112
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:38,019
Xiao Suisui, what are you doing?

113
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:39,500
You're pressing on my leg! Get down.

114
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,540
(It hurts...)

115
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,460
(I can feel my leg again?)

116
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:54,559
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

117
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:58,399
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

118
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:01,919
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

119
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:04,880
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

120
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:09,399
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

121
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:13,160
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

122
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,559
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

123
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:20,600
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

124
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:29,879
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

125
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:33,519
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

126
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:37,239
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

127
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:40,879
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

128
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:44,559
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

129
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,479
♪Endlessly flowing♪

130
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:52,680
♪Good fortune♪
